{"tid":812484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺中國人人都想發達，呢個思想好可悲","createTime":"2018-09-09T16:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T03:35:07.000Z","uid":123335,"like":61,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"925f5cd25298fe0bfb817f3e3e36c5aab9c56a52","tid":812484,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"中國有13億人<br />\n人人都想發達 <br />\n13億人都想發達<br />\n13億人都想做老闆 <br />\n13億人都想做大型上市公司CEO <br />\n<br />\n呢種思想真係好撚on9 <br />\n根本係唔會work <br />\n一定有輸家 <br />\n而輸家幾乎係佔95% up <br />\n意思係有 95% 既人成世都係做Loser , 活係失敗之中<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句<br />\n呢種「人人都想發達」既思想，真係害撚死人 <br />\n害撚死95%社會上既人"},{"pid":"0b7b4337ae20ca29d15938cc6c63a595c91a0312","tid":812484,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f6f7d08423c625382cf7324752cdfe98047f50","tid":812484,"uid":19454,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/001506_69d9fd7b829ba572deabc9dfaddc4697.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F001506_69d9fd7b829ba572deabc9dfaddc4697.JPG&h=5df7b3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/001506_cd822c3833a03f98c9ee32789ce94bef.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F001506_cd822c3833a03f98c9ee32789ce94bef.JPG&h=024477f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/001506_411e658671a068c13075cd80ba941e60.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F001506_411e658671a068c13075cd80ba941e60.JPG&h=5c9310ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc62e58318829874ea3f985bc92482f4b9f34d5b","tid":812484,"uid":45830,"like":4,"disli