","tid":812484,"uid":104443,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"中國古代四家之中，以法家最為不近人情，而儒家就太注重輩份尊卑，反而道家同墨家係最和平最理性嘅思想，強調小國寡民，唔追求名利，過自然生活"},{"pid":"cb9d5f3d76191b2e75df8f1e239f43474be3ae63","tid":812484,"uid":104443,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:50:35.000Z","msg":"可惜歷代只重儒法而輕道墨"},{"pid":"58e57cc38ebb2fb72a6ee46047273e525f775c21","tid":812484,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:53:13.000Z","msg":"其實管理咁大群人係好難，<br />\n管理十三億人，呢種方法係方便好多<br />\n<br />\n西歐國家能夠咁發達因為人少，先令到管理成本下降，因材施教"},{"pid":"eb76c6dde71d01be5e3476cfae0840360fff42a3","tid":812484,"uid":33481,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"58e57cc38ebb2fb72a6ee46047273e525f775c21","tid":812484,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:53:13.000Z","msg":"其實管理咁大群人係好難，<br />\n管理十三億人，呢種方法係方便好多<br />\n<br />\n西歐國家能夠咁發達因為人少，先令到管理成本下降，因材施教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:16:34.000Z","msg":"所以分裂最好"},{"pid":"c1c48fde482e25975ee82794bb0b0405caec17b6","tid":812484,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f6f7d08423c625382cf7324752cdfe98047f50","tid":812484,"uid":19454,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/001506_69d9fd7b829ba572deabc9dfaddc4697.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F001506_69d9fd7b829ba572deabc9dfaddc4697.JPG&h=5df7b3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/001506_cd822c3833a03f98c9ee32789ce94bef.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F001506_cd822c3833a03f98c9ee32789ce94bef.JPG&h=024477f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/001506_411e658671a068c13075cd80ba941e60.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F001506_411e658671a068c13075cd80ba941e60.JPG&h=5c9310ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:17:57.000Z","msg":"態度正確"},{"pid":"2ad37a805fb06bbf984b1ca4af21d31cb2523124","tid":812484,"uid":838,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:31:13.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲照下鏡，睇下自己個樣，同埋睇下你本銀行存摺有幾多錢先啦<br />\n<br />\n世界好公平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果人人都心想事成<br />\n<br />\n會天下大亂<br />\n<br />\n世上總要有你啲咁嘅廢人"},{"pid":"06dcc63b74ce2bd4a988a1e412bff314b5b45c7c","tid":812484,"uid":59030,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T19:12:26.000Z","msg":"係澳洲見啲人個個禮拜一出糧就去賭場fing晒佢<br />\n個個mall都有幾間旅行社<br />\n人地唔洗發達都過緊中國人發達想過既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a35e67d0d9e7afd92fc0437b50ed4b5c4c2c76","tid":812484,"uid":193915,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T19:31:25.000Z","msg":"唔止中國，美國自從1930s great depression之後都變緊係咁，好大原因係金融業坐大同扭曲，施財技賺嘅錢同其他行業唔成正比"},{"pid":"a134b56ed08a02b73579a77e9829d40793d45a5c","tid":812484,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T00:01:53.000Z","msg":"結論：樓主永遠都係窮撚"},{"pid":"6151692988e7d75a8e993fa7da9f6adb143ee888","tid":812484,"uid":3112,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:08:55.000Z","msg":"樓主唔buy資本主義，大可以去英國以外既歐洲喎。<br />\n福利好，收入差距唔大，有錢佬要同政府平分收入。名校/大企業家收人又不論家底，只睇成績/interview。但係歷史證明左玩社會主義or共產就係死路一條。<br />\n<br />\n人係有慾望、野心同私心既動物。你忍心睇住賺返黎既錢比政府拎去養難民，養新移民？<br />\n你又忍心睇住自己上左位，人工係高左，同時稅都高左好多。拉返埋同你條𡃁既人工可能係差唔多？歐洲精英係得唔到佢地應有嘅待遇。<br />\n<br />\n所以歐洲佬所幻想既完美世界係唔會存在於現實。而美帝靠金融與科技建立既帝國，先至符合人性。"},{"pid":"556216d3036d6e6d4f1b80435827476ec8948144","tid":812484,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58e57cc38ebb2fb72a6ee46047273e525f775c21","tid":812484,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:53:13.000Z","msg":"其實管理咁大群人係好難，<br />\n管理十三億人，呢種方法係方便好多<br />\n<br />\n西歐國家能夠咁發達因為人少，先令到管理成本下降，因材施教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"學歐洲咁折做小國未得"},{"pid":"2f24835515beb531eb54b8c00ae6127a7839bf9c","tid":812484,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"因為有d嘢係要好有錢先享受到"},{"pid":"1945faa872802666cb1d5a96b98b20f3b6937811","tid":812484,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T10:58:23.000Z","msg":"一係就想發達<br />\n一係就想去其他國家痴人哋啲福利"}]}